1
00:01:25,200 --> 00:01:29,980
[Youthful Glory]

2
00:01:30,100 --> 00:01:32,910
[Episode 3]

3
00:01:35,240 --> 00:01:36,360
How can you make sure

4
00:01:36,360 --> 00:01:38,360
that she won't appear again

5
00:01:38,560 --> 00:01:39,920
or cause trouble?

6
00:01:39,920 --> 00:01:40,600
Well...

7
00:01:42,360 --> 00:01:43,160
I...

8
00:01:45,440 --> 00:01:47,060
She has to vanish.

9
00:01:51,160 --> 00:01:52,960
Vanish! Vanish!

10
00:02:12,410 --> 00:02:13,640
Miss Bai,

11
00:02:14,160 --> 00:02:15,160
please let me go.

12
00:02:15,270 --> 00:02:16,230
I beg you.

13
00:02:18,280 --> 00:02:18,960
Hand her over.

14
00:02:18,960 --> 00:02:19,840
I...

15
00:02:20,079 --> 00:02:21,400
I've told you many times

16
00:02:21,400 --> 00:02:22,890
that I don't know where she is.

17
00:02:22,890 --> 00:02:23,650
I don't care.

18
00:02:24,079 --> 00:02:25,640
She was last seen here.

19
00:02:25,660 --> 00:02:27,120
You owe me an explanation.

20
00:02:33,160 --> 00:02:33,880
My Lady,

21
00:02:33,880 --> 00:02:34,400
His Grace and Her Grace

22
00:02:34,400 --> 00:02:35,480
are worried sick

23
00:02:35,480 --> 00:02:36,280
since you're still not home.

24
00:02:36,280 --> 00:02:38,079
The house is a complete mess now!

25
00:02:38,550 --> 00:02:39,340
Please go home.

26
00:02:39,340 --> 00:02:40,520
Your house is a complete mess now.

27
00:02:40,520 --> 00:02:41,240
Nanzhi,

28
00:02:41,490 --> 00:02:43,090
go get my father.

29
00:02:43,110 --> 00:02:44,310
I look forward to

30
00:02:44,340 --> 00:02:45,820
hearing what you will say

31
00:02:45,840 --> 00:02:47,440
to the duke.

32
00:02:50,930 --> 00:02:52,160
I believe Miss Bai

33
00:02:52,260 --> 00:02:53,900
can make a great eagle tamer.

34
00:02:56,420 --> 00:03:02,630
[Qingfeng Inn]

35
00:03:10,230 --> 00:03:11,830
Here are your noodles.

36
00:03:13,640 --> 00:03:14,680
Please enjoy.

37
00:03:17,560 --> 00:03:18,600
Miss, be quick.

38
00:03:18,640 --> 00:03:20,300
There is still a long way to go.

39
00:03:20,450 --> 00:03:21,220
We've been walking

40
00:03:21,220 --> 00:03:22,750
non-stop for the whole day.

41
00:03:23,090 --> 00:03:24,570
The sun is setting now.

42
00:03:25,079 --> 00:03:26,140
Can't we take a rest

43
00:03:26,260 --> 00:03:27,820
and spend the night here?

44
00:03:40,180 --> 00:03:42,110
There's no meat at all.

45
00:03:42,430 --> 00:03:43,480
Did my aunt ask you

46
00:03:43,480 --> 00:03:44,680
to treat me like this?

47
00:03:45,140 --> 00:03:47,020
It's her order for us to rush.

48
00:03:47,050 --> 00:03:47,990
You can get some rest

49
00:03:47,990 --> 00:03:49,260
and receive prenatal care

50
00:03:49,260 --> 00:03:50,560
when we reach the destination.

51
00:03:50,560 --> 00:03:52,240
Where exactly has my aunt

52
00:03:52,240 --> 00:03:53,600
arranged for me to stay?

53
00:03:54,210 --> 00:03:55,740
The countryside of Lizhou.

54
00:03:55,990 --> 00:03:57,050
Don't worry, miss.

55
00:03:57,170 --> 00:03:58,079
When the noise dies down,

56
00:03:58,079 --> 00:04:00,940
the young master will bring you back to the capital.

57
00:04:03,400 --> 00:04:05,110
Waiter, get me some steamed buns,

58
00:04:05,110 --> 00:04:06,370
and a bowl of lamb soup!

59
00:04:06,540 --> 00:04:07,340
Got it!

60
00:04:08,000 --> 00:04:10,090
Why so generous today?

61
00:04:10,120 --> 00:04:12,320
Did you find a treasure on the mountain?

62
00:04:16,779 --> 00:04:17,810
I just dug this out.

63
00:04:17,810 --> 00:04:19,430
I'll sell it to a pharmacy later.

64
00:04:19,430 --> 00:04:20,980
It'll surely bring me a fortune!

65
00:04:20,980 --> 00:04:22,370
It is indeed a treasure.

66
00:04:23,930 --> 00:04:25,070
I'll go get you some steamed buns.

67
00:04:25,070 --> 00:04:25,870
Go, go, go.

68
00:04:32,850 --> 00:04:34,830
How much is the ginseng?

69
00:04:38,010 --> 00:04:39,610
Ma'am, you have such a good eye.

70
00:04:39,610 --> 00:04:40,210
50 taels.

71
00:04:40,800 --> 00:04:41,600
That much?

72
00:04:42,570 --> 00:04:44,700
This is a complete piece of

73
00:04:44,720 --> 00:04:46,250
century-old wild ginseng.

74
00:04:48,140 --> 00:04:50,090
I happen to be in the market

75
00:04:50,159 --> 00:04:51,280
for some ginseng.

76
00:04:52,120 --> 00:04:53,720
Why don't you sell

77
00:04:53,720 --> 00:04:54,760
this to me?

78
00:04:59,460 --> 00:05:01,640
This is too little.

79
00:05:02,770 --> 00:05:03,790
100 taels!

80
00:05:08,170 --> 00:05:11,390
[Ming Chu]
[Marquis of Qing'an's third daughter]

81
00:05:08,810 --> 00:05:10,610
I'll take the ginseng.

82
00:05:13,030 --> 00:05:14,410
You take this back, ma'am.

83
00:05:14,410 --> 00:05:15,020
But...

84
00:05:15,320 --> 00:05:15,880
But...

85
00:05:16,690 --> 00:05:18,190
Miss, you really have a good eye.

86
00:05:18,190 --> 00:05:19,190
This is yours now.

87
00:05:22,880 --> 00:05:23,560
Mom,

88
00:05:23,580 --> 00:05:25,180
such high-quality ginseng is rarely seen.

89
00:05:24,380 --> 00:05:27,470
[Madam Liu]
[Marquis of Jing'an's concubine]

90
00:05:25,210 --> 00:05:26,940
I'll give it to Father as a gift.

91
00:05:28,490 --> 00:05:30,230
I offered to buy the ginseng first.

92
00:05:30,230 --> 00:05:31,030
Miss,

93
00:05:31,060 --> 00:05:32,770
you can't barge in like this.

94
00:05:34,800 --> 00:05:35,600
Wait!

95
00:05:35,750 --> 00:05:37,540
How dare you stand in my way.

96
00:05:37,680 --> 00:05:39,409
My whip will teach you a lesson!

97
00:06:03,970 --> 00:06:05,270
Thank you, sir.

98
00:06:06,750 --> 00:06:08,110
She was unreasonable

99
00:06:08,160 --> 00:06:09,380
and standing in my way.

100
00:06:09,380 --> 00:06:10,980
Even if she had got hurt,

101
00:06:11,130 --> 00:06:12,530
it would be her own fault.

102
00:06:14,200 --> 00:06:15,760
Take her to a room for some rest.

103
00:06:15,760 --> 00:06:16,200
Yes.

104
00:06:24,900 --> 00:06:25,780
Sir, are you

105
00:06:25,800 --> 00:06:27,210
spending the night here?

106
00:06:27,270 --> 00:06:29,000
How about I treat you to a drink?

107
00:06:29,920 --> 00:06:30,800
In fact, I...

108
00:06:30,800 --> 00:06:31,800
All that glitters

109
00:06:32,520 --> 00:06:33,560
is not gold.

110
00:06:42,000 --> 00:06:42,800
Mom,

111
00:06:43,360 --> 00:06:44,400
what did he

112
00:06:44,490 --> 00:06:45,510
mean by that?

113
00:06:45,650 --> 00:06:47,130
Who cares?

114
00:06:48,360 --> 00:06:49,659
Listen up,

115
00:06:49,690 --> 00:06:51,390
we finally came back in town.

116
00:06:51,409 --> 00:06:52,880
You must be on your best behavior

117
00:06:52,880 --> 00:06:54,630
and not stir up trouble again.

118
00:06:55,470 --> 00:06:57,790
Our priority is to obtain permission

119
00:06:57,860 --> 00:06:59,140
to settle down here

120
00:06:59,680 --> 00:07:00,880
and to avoid going

121
00:07:00,880 --> 00:07:02,410
back to Yangxi Prefecture.

122
00:07:06,070 --> 00:07:06,970
Mom,

123
00:07:07,320 --> 00:07:08,780
the rest of the journey will take only a few hours.

124
00:07:08,780 --> 00:07:09,200
Why don't we

125
00:07:09,200 --> 00:07:10,600
sleep here tonight,

126
00:07:10,620 --> 00:07:12,080
and hit the road tomorrow?

127
00:07:16,210 --> 00:07:18,580
[Spring Room]

128
00:07:32,880 --> 00:07:33,560
Who is it?

129
00:07:34,830 --> 00:07:37,220
I'm Ming Tan, Marquis of Jing'an's fourth daughter.

130
00:07:37,220 --> 00:07:38,220
It's you.

131
00:07:39,159 --> 00:07:40,490
What are you doing here?

132
00:07:40,560 --> 00:07:42,030
Taking you back to the capital.

133
00:07:42,030 --> 00:07:43,370
Don't hurt me!

134
00:07:43,560 --> 00:07:44,280
I'm pregnant

135
00:07:44,280 --> 00:07:45,409
with Zixuan's baby.

136
00:07:45,520 --> 00:07:46,400
I can't stop you

137
00:07:46,400 --> 00:07:47,360
from marrying him.

138
00:07:47,360 --> 00:07:47,960
But he and I

139
00:07:47,960 --> 00:07:49,159
are truly in love.

140
00:07:49,180 --> 00:07:50,560
Whether you two

141
00:07:50,560 --> 00:07:51,640
are in love or not

142
00:07:51,640 --> 00:07:52,880
doesn't concern me.

143
00:07:54,730 --> 00:07:56,800
Then why are you taking me back to the capital?

144
00:07:56,800 --> 00:07:57,659
My plan is...

145
00:08:00,250 --> 00:08:00,860
It's her!

146
00:08:02,260 --> 00:08:03,320
Take action!

147
00:08:27,990 --> 00:08:29,620
Weak though you are,

148
00:08:29,740 --> 00:08:31,170
you risked your life anyway.

149
00:08:31,170 --> 00:08:33,250
What kind of act was it?

150
00:08:33,360 --> 00:08:34,679
A heroic one.

151
00:08:34,860 --> 00:08:36,260
Reckless, I'd say.

152
00:08:36,350 --> 00:08:37,630
How was I being...

153
00:08:42,789 --> 00:08:44,010
Do you really think

154
00:08:44,530 --> 00:08:46,010
the Liang family will take you

155
00:08:46,010 --> 00:08:47,610
back after you reach Lizhou?

156
00:08:48,300 --> 00:08:49,160
You're not sent

157
00:08:49,160 --> 00:08:50,380
by Zixuan to protect me.

158
00:08:50,380 --> 00:08:51,550
Who are you?

159
00:08:52,740 --> 00:08:53,200
What...

160
00:08:53,390 --> 00:08:55,280
What is going on here?

161
00:08:55,980 --> 00:08:57,980
Those people attempted to kill you.

162
00:08:58,930 --> 00:09:00,060
Do you still believe

163
00:09:00,480 --> 00:09:01,440
the Liang family will

164
00:09:01,440 --> 00:09:02,320
honor their promise?

165
00:09:02,320 --> 00:09:03,320
They will!

166
00:09:03,680 --> 00:09:05,080
My aunt promised to

167
00:09:05,480 --> 00:09:06,960
bring me and my baby back

168
00:09:06,980 --> 00:09:08,130
to the capital city

169
00:09:08,160 --> 00:09:09,310
after Zixuan's wedding.

170
00:09:09,310 --> 00:09:10,630
She wouldn't lie to me.

171
00:09:11,160 --> 00:09:12,360
Your aunt has planned to

172
00:09:12,360 --> 00:09:14,690
marry you to their housekeeper in Lizhou.

173
00:09:14,780 --> 00:09:15,920
She won't let you back

174
00:09:15,920 --> 00:09:17,050
to the capital city.

175
00:09:17,540 --> 00:09:18,670
That's impossible.

176
00:09:18,760 --> 00:09:20,590
My dad has given her many favors.

177
00:09:20,620 --> 00:09:22,480
They wouldn't treat me like this!

178
00:09:28,500 --> 00:09:29,900
You have two options now.

179
00:09:30,800 --> 00:09:31,280
One,

180
00:09:31,950 --> 00:09:33,950
marry their housekeeper in Lizhou.

181
00:09:34,090 --> 00:09:34,660
Two,

182
00:09:35,220 --> 00:09:36,220
follow me back to

183
00:09:36,730 --> 00:09:37,690
the Liang family

184
00:09:38,350 --> 00:09:39,430
and seek justice.

185
00:09:42,130 --> 00:09:43,710
There's a third option.

186
00:09:44,330 --> 00:09:45,460
You can come with me.

187
00:09:45,570 --> 00:09:47,520
If you help me cancel my engagement,

188
00:09:47,520 --> 00:09:48,620
I'll do everything to assist

189
00:09:48,620 --> 00:09:49,770
you in marrying Zixuan

190
00:09:49,770 --> 00:09:51,450
and becoming his legal wife.

191
00:09:51,520 --> 00:09:52,320
Legal wife?

192
00:09:53,000 --> 00:09:54,460
The Liang family wants her dead.

193
00:09:54,460 --> 00:09:56,240
You think Liang Zixuan will marry her?

194
00:09:56,240 --> 00:09:57,290
-I...
-Cut it out!

195
00:09:57,970 --> 00:10:00,400
G-Get me a midwife now!

196
00:10:02,140 --> 00:10:03,720
Go get a midwife!

197
00:10:06,880 --> 00:10:08,360
Push! Harder!

198
00:10:08,360 --> 00:10:09,220
Push!

199
00:10:09,560 --> 00:10:10,560
Hold your breath and push!

200
00:10:10,560 --> 00:10:11,560
Tell Yu to find a quiet place

201
00:10:11,560 --> 00:10:12,560
in the capital city.

202
00:10:12,560 --> 00:10:13,360
Keep pushing like this.

203
00:10:13,360 --> 00:10:14,780
When Zhu'er's father arrives,

204
00:10:14,780 --> 00:10:15,840
put him and his daughter

205
00:10:15,840 --> 00:10:16,720
in confinement.

206
00:10:16,720 --> 00:10:17,680
Push. Harder!

207
00:10:17,680 --> 00:10:18,360
Got it.

208
00:10:19,960 --> 00:10:21,640
Miss, don't just stand there.

209
00:10:21,640 --> 00:10:23,120
Come on, help me with it.

210
00:10:23,910 --> 00:10:24,520
Okay!

211
00:10:24,520 --> 00:10:25,840
Look at you, so fussy.

212
00:10:25,840 --> 00:10:27,360
Go get me a cloth.

213
00:10:27,360 --> 00:10:28,360
Hurry up!

214
00:10:28,360 --> 00:10:29,360
She is really in labor now.

215
00:10:29,360 --> 00:10:29,920
Okay. I got it!

216
00:10:29,920 --> 00:10:31,000
Relax. Just relax.

217
00:10:31,070 --> 00:10:31,800
Here you are.

218
00:10:33,120 --> 00:10:34,400
A waiter told me that lady

219
00:10:34,400 --> 00:10:35,580
had gone into labor early,

220
00:10:35,580 --> 00:10:37,420
so I brought this ginseng to her.

221
00:10:37,960 --> 00:10:38,920
Push harder.

222
00:10:40,920 --> 00:10:41,720
My mother and I

223
00:10:41,760 --> 00:10:43,120
just came back from Yangxi Prefecture.

224
00:10:43,120 --> 00:10:44,650
I don’t know much about

225
00:10:44,680 --> 00:10:45,620
the local customs.

226
00:10:45,620 --> 00:10:47,020
I acted rude before.

227
00:10:47,050 --> 00:10:47,970
I must've made

228
00:10:47,990 --> 00:10:49,710
a bad first impression.

229
00:10:49,770 --> 00:10:50,570
I don't care.

230
00:10:52,360 --> 00:10:53,760
Hold your breath.

231
00:10:53,790 --> 00:10:54,720
Bear with the pain.

232
00:10:54,720 --> 00:10:56,840
Don't scream. Channel the energy elsewhere.

233
00:10:56,840 --> 00:10:57,720
Take a deep breath.

234
00:10:57,720 --> 00:10:58,760
Hold it and push.

235
00:11:00,690 --> 00:11:01,730
She...

236
00:11:04,750 --> 00:11:05,920
She has fainted.

237
00:11:08,460 --> 00:11:09,140
Ma'am!

238
00:11:09,300 --> 00:11:09,980
Ma'am!

239
00:11:10,520 --> 00:11:11,120
-Ma'am!
-Look.

240
00:11:11,120 --> 00:11:12,450
I came here just in time.

241
00:11:12,570 --> 00:11:13,680
I can sell this ginseng to her

242
00:11:13,680 --> 00:11:14,620
at the original price.

243
00:11:14,620 --> 00:11:15,080
Ma'am!

244
00:11:15,080 --> 00:11:17,750
I, Ming Chu, am always a kind

245
00:11:17,880 --> 00:11:19,770
and charitable person.

246
00:11:19,960 --> 00:11:20,440
Ma'am!

247
00:11:20,440 --> 00:11:21,280
Ming Chu?

248
00:11:21,770 --> 00:11:22,900
Why is she here?

249
00:11:23,800 --> 00:11:24,790
Miss,

250
00:11:24,820 --> 00:11:26,290
is there ginseng?

251
00:11:26,310 --> 00:11:28,430
Fetch it and feed it to this lady.

252
00:11:28,560 --> 00:11:29,780
We must wake her up right away,

253
00:11:29,780 --> 00:11:31,780
or the baby's life will be in danger!

254
00:11:32,290 --> 00:11:33,210
Hurry!

255
00:11:40,160 --> 00:11:41,980
I kindly brought the ginseng here.

256
00:11:41,980 --> 00:11:42,920
It's only fair that I get

257
00:11:42,920 --> 00:11:43,880
paid.

258
00:11:44,070 --> 00:11:46,230
Sir, you should take my side.

259
00:11:46,760 --> 00:11:48,760
Sir, save your wife's life.

260
00:11:48,760 --> 00:11:50,560
Pay for the ginseng now, please.

261
00:11:51,550 --> 00:11:54,040
The woman in labor is your wife?

262
00:11:54,590 --> 00:11:55,270
Sir,

263
00:11:55,470 --> 00:11:56,580
your wife ran away from home

264
00:11:56,580 --> 00:11:58,080
out of anger when she discovered

265
00:11:58,080 --> 00:11:59,540
your mistress.

266
00:11:59,560 --> 00:12:01,890
How are you going to explain to your father

267
00:12:02,020 --> 00:12:04,040
if his grandchild dies?

268
00:12:15,160 --> 00:12:16,840
I-Is it all?

269
00:12:16,840 --> 00:12:18,710
This is how much the ginseng is worth.

270
00:12:18,710 --> 00:12:19,680
How do you know it isn't

271
00:12:19,680 --> 00:12:20,520
worth more?

272
00:12:20,520 --> 00:12:21,520
It obviously isn't.

273
00:12:21,520 --> 00:12:22,160
B-But I did

274
00:12:22,160 --> 00:12:22,920
spend 100 taels...

275
00:12:22,920 --> 00:12:23,960
The seller lied,

276
00:12:24,080 --> 00:12:25,540
and you fell for his trick.

277
00:12:25,680 --> 00:12:26,940
The blame is all yours.

278
00:12:34,480 --> 00:12:35,480
The baby is born!

279
00:12:35,480 --> 00:12:36,360
Here is the baby!

280
00:12:36,360 --> 00:12:38,160
The mother and son are both safe.

281
00:12:41,290 --> 00:12:42,640
I know you and Liang Zixuan

282
00:12:42,640 --> 00:12:43,680
are in love.

283
00:12:44,410 --> 00:12:45,870
But why are you the only one

284
00:12:46,210 --> 00:12:48,210
to make compromises every time?

285
00:12:49,360 --> 00:12:50,520
I would gladly

286
00:12:51,210 --> 00:12:52,850
do anything for him.

287
00:12:53,590 --> 00:12:55,370
I've decided to cancel the engagement.

288
00:12:55,370 --> 00:12:57,440
You should come back to the capital with me,

289
00:12:57,440 --> 00:12:58,400
so you can fight

290
00:12:58,520 --> 00:13:00,200
for what you deserve.

291
00:13:01,320 --> 00:13:03,180
Are you sure of canceling the engagement?

292
00:13:03,180 --> 00:13:05,580
I don't love him. Why should I marry him?

293
00:13:06,570 --> 00:13:08,120
Men would make sacrifices

