a word since you came in.

587
00:26:13,520 --> 00:26:14,670
I wonder what your

588
00:26:15,160 --> 00:26:17,760
opinions are on this matter.

589
00:26:20,240 --> 00:26:21,040
Your Majesty,

590
00:26:21,770 --> 00:26:23,770
the truth of this case must be found out,

591
00:26:23,770 --> 00:26:25,800
or Dingbei Army will have low morale.

592
00:26:25,800 --> 00:26:27,460
Even the people in our country

593
00:26:27,480 --> 00:26:28,840
will be disheartened.

594
00:26:29,520 --> 00:26:30,360
I think

595
00:26:30,520 --> 00:26:32,280
letting Prince of Dingbei stay here

596
00:26:32,280 --> 00:26:33,840
to supervise the investigation

597
00:26:33,840 --> 00:26:35,920
is the best way to relieve

598
00:26:35,940 --> 00:26:37,350
the soldiers' worries.

599
00:26:40,070 --> 00:26:41,680
Right Chancellor, what are the odds?

600
00:26:41,680 --> 00:26:43,600
We're finally on the same page.

601
00:26:44,240 --> 00:26:45,040
Your Majesty,

602
00:26:45,240 --> 00:26:47,720
Prince of Dingbei's decisiveness

603
00:26:47,740 --> 00:26:49,160
is exactly what we need

604
00:26:49,160 --> 00:26:50,370
to work out this case.

605
00:26:50,390 --> 00:26:53,270
The Court of Review alone is not enough.

606
00:26:53,890 --> 00:26:54,970
Your Majesty,

607
00:26:55,040 --> 00:26:55,920
investigations must be

608
00:26:55,920 --> 00:26:57,460
conducted in accordance to the law.

609
00:26:57,460 --> 00:26:59,420
Officials can't do whatever they want.

610
00:26:59,420 --> 00:27:00,990
Prince of Dingbei came to the capital without permission.

611
00:27:00,990 --> 00:27:02,260
This is a serious crime.

612
00:27:02,260 --> 00:27:04,220
Your Majesty, please be fair

613
00:27:04,250 --> 00:27:05,650
and punish law breakers.

614
00:27:07,560 --> 00:27:08,820
It is my imperial edict

615
00:27:08,920 --> 00:27:11,320
that Prince of Dingbei will be beaten
20 times with a rod for coming

616
00:27:11,320 --> 00:27:12,840
to the capital without my order.

617
00:27:12,840 --> 00:27:13,840
He will receive

618
00:27:14,090 --> 00:27:16,300
further punishment when the embezzlement

619
00:27:16,300 --> 00:27:17,700
case is solved.

620
00:27:18,320 --> 00:27:19,240
Yes.

621
00:27:19,560 --> 00:27:20,490
Your Majesty...

622
00:27:23,550 --> 00:27:27,410
[Capital Garrison]

623
00:27:33,880 --> 00:27:34,680
Eleven.

624
00:27:35,400 --> 00:27:36,560
Twelve.

625
00:27:36,880 --> 00:27:38,000
Thirteen.

626
00:27:38,280 --> 00:27:39,360
Fourteen.

627
00:27:39,870 --> 00:27:40,910
Fifteen.

628
00:27:41,560 --> 00:27:42,640
Sixteen.

629
00:27:43,400 --> 00:27:44,400
Seventeen.

630
00:27:44,880 --> 00:27:45,880
Eighteen.

631
00:27:46,560 --> 00:27:47,440
Nineteen.

632
00:27:48,160 --> 00:27:49,320
Twenty!

633
00:27:53,200 --> 00:27:54,680
You've made a scapegoat

634
00:27:54,710 --> 00:27:55,950
out of a wooden dummy.

635
00:28:02,640 --> 00:28:03,500
Your Highness.

636
00:28:03,680 --> 00:28:05,010
The punishment is over.

637
00:28:05,080 --> 00:28:07,800
I'm leaving for the palace now.

638
00:28:07,800 --> 00:28:10,040
Your Highness, do not forget this lesson,

639
00:28:10,040 --> 00:28:11,570
and please work on the case.

640
00:28:13,520 --> 00:28:14,780
Thank you, Eunuch Liu.

641
00:28:22,560 --> 00:28:23,560
Oh, right, Xu.

642
00:28:23,580 --> 00:28:24,820
Yu complained to me,

643
00:28:24,870 --> 00:28:25,880
saying that you took

644
00:28:25,880 --> 00:28:27,360
Miss Ming away for no reason.

645
00:28:27,360 --> 00:28:28,480
As a result, he was tortured

646
00:28:28,480 --> 00:28:29,480
badly by Miss Bai.

647
00:28:30,040 --> 00:28:30,840
You two...

648
00:28:31,820 --> 00:28:33,080
Where did you

649
00:28:33,080 --> 00:28:34,160
take Miss Ming to?

650
00:28:33,730 --> 00:28:34,210
[Ledgers]

651
00:28:34,420 --> 00:28:35,420
I went out of town

652
00:28:35,880 --> 00:28:36,840
for this stuff.

653
00:28:38,370 --> 00:28:40,170
The money that the Duke of Ling embezzled

654
00:28:40,170 --> 00:28:41,970
was handled by Zhu'er's father.

655
00:28:42,190 --> 00:28:43,400
Only a small portion of it was

656
00:28:43,400 --> 00:28:45,320
in the secret chamber of the duke's house.

657
00:28:45,320 --> 00:28:47,130
I've sent people to search Zhu'er's house.

658
00:28:47,130 --> 00:28:49,250
Her father and she have confessed.

659
00:28:49,380 --> 00:28:51,340
[Ledgers]

660
00:28:50,720 --> 00:28:51,720
Solid evidence.

661
00:28:51,880 --> 00:28:53,320
When will you write the Duke of Ling up?

662
00:28:53,320 --> 00:28:55,060
Marquis of Jing'an will reach the capital today.

663
00:28:55,060 --> 00:28:56,260
Without further ado,

664
00:28:56,830 --> 00:28:57,970
I'll take action today.

665
00:28:57,970 --> 00:29:03,840
[Marquis of Jing'an's Mansion]

666
00:29:06,510 --> 00:29:10,030
[Ming Tingyuan]
[Marquis of Jing'an]

667
00:29:13,520 --> 00:29:14,320
Father!

668
00:29:13,790 --> 00:29:17,400
[Rising Sun]

669
00:29:16,340 --> 00:29:17,810
Father, you're finally back.

670
00:29:17,810 --> 00:29:19,400
You were away for only one day.

671
00:29:19,400 --> 00:29:20,360
Chu has been

672
00:29:20,360 --> 00:29:21,640
missing you the entire time.

673
00:29:21,640 --> 00:29:22,880
After you were summoned to the palace,

674
00:29:22,880 --> 00:29:25,090
no one could practice whipping with me.

675
00:29:25,310 --> 00:29:26,190
Later on,

676
00:29:26,240 --> 00:29:28,040
let's have a friendly fight

677
00:29:28,040 --> 00:29:28,880
as practice.

678
00:29:30,520 --> 00:29:32,980
How are you adapting to the new environment?

679
00:29:33,370 --> 00:29:35,850
I'm cozy at home now, don't you see?

680
00:29:36,080 --> 00:29:38,080
However, no one welcomed Mom and me

681
00:29:38,080 --> 00:29:39,680
as we came back here.

682
00:29:39,900 --> 00:29:41,720
The servants are rude

683
00:29:41,740 --> 00:29:42,810
and disrespectful.

684
00:29:42,810 --> 00:29:43,760
Father,

685
00:29:43,810 --> 00:29:45,480
are Mom and I

686
00:29:45,510 --> 00:29:47,070
not part of the Ming family?

687
00:29:49,360 --> 00:29:51,440
Welcome back, My Lord.

688
00:29:52,580 --> 00:29:53,750
I beg for your forgiveness.

689
00:29:53,750 --> 00:29:55,350
Fourth Miss is busy

690
00:29:55,380 --> 00:29:56,640
managing the mansion.

691
00:29:56,790 --> 00:29:57,590
That is why

692
00:29:57,640 --> 00:29:58,680
she couldn't welcome the arrival

693
00:29:58,680 --> 00:29:59,840
of Third Miss and Madam Liu.

694
00:29:59,840 --> 00:30:01,190
But she told me

695
00:30:01,210 --> 00:30:03,330
to take good care of them.

696
00:30:03,360 --> 00:30:04,860
Fourth Miss has had Yiyun House

697
00:30:04,860 --> 00:30:05,740
redecorated

698
00:30:05,770 --> 00:30:07,500
and arranged competent servants

699
00:30:07,500 --> 00:30:09,300
for Third Miss and Madam Liu

700
00:30:09,330 --> 00:30:11,370
to ensure their comfort.

701
00:30:11,700 --> 00:30:12,600
See,

702
00:30:12,760 --> 00:30:14,560
things have been well prepared.

703
00:30:15,400 --> 00:30:16,280
Where is Tan?

704
00:30:17,080 --> 00:30:17,960
My Lord,

705
00:30:18,000 --> 00:30:19,840
Fourth Miss was thrilled to know

706
00:30:19,840 --> 00:30:20,820
about your return.

707
00:30:20,820 --> 00:30:22,220
She said she would make

708
00:30:22,250 --> 00:30:24,170
your favorite dishes on her own.

709
00:30:24,680 --> 00:30:25,800
I've sent someone

710
00:30:25,800 --> 00:30:27,360
to invite Mr. Bai over.

711
00:30:27,360 --> 00:30:28,490
He'll be there soon.

712
00:30:29,000 --> 00:30:30,080
After my long stay in the palace,

713
00:30:30,080 --> 00:30:31,080
I'm feeling hungry.

714
00:30:30,660 --> 00:30:32,680
[Rising Sun]

715
00:30:31,080 --> 00:30:31,800
Let's go.

716
00:30:32,240 --> 00:30:33,040
Father,

717
00:30:33,200 --> 00:30:33,890
why not wash

718
00:30:33,920 --> 00:30:35,700
our hands before eating?

719
00:30:35,240 --> 00:30:38,990
[Rising Sun]

720
00:30:36,590 --> 00:30:37,150
Okay.

721
00:30:42,360 --> 00:30:44,180
The plating is not good enough.

722
00:30:44,220 --> 00:30:46,290
Have it replated.

723
00:30:46,560 --> 00:30:47,360
Yes.

724
00:30:50,080 --> 00:30:52,200
Tan, you seem mysterious.

725
00:30:52,220 --> 00:30:53,180
Where did you go?

726
00:30:54,070 --> 00:30:55,450
Did something happen?

727
00:30:55,480 --> 00:30:57,010
Don't hide secrets from me.

728
00:30:57,530 --> 00:30:58,250
Actually,

729
00:30:58,280 --> 00:30:59,560
I went after Zhu'er.

730
00:30:59,600 --> 00:31:01,280
Alone?

731
00:31:01,280 --> 00:31:02,380
How bold of you!

732
00:31:02,850 --> 00:31:03,890
It's a long story.

733
00:31:03,960 --> 00:31:04,520
Let's have

734
00:31:04,520 --> 00:31:05,680
a gathering feast first.

735
00:31:05,680 --> 00:31:06,920
I'll tell you

736
00:31:07,300 --> 00:31:09,160
the details later.

737
00:31:11,680 --> 00:31:12,270
Let's go.

738
00:31:12,920 --> 00:31:13,560
Come with me

739
00:31:13,560 --> 00:31:14,560
to check if the stew is ready.

740
00:31:14,560 --> 00:31:15,560
Do we have to?

741
00:31:16,010 --> 00:31:17,070
Just come with me.

742
00:31:17,610 --> 00:31:18,300
Ms. Zhang,

743
00:31:18,320 --> 00:31:20,620
are the rest of the issues taken care of?

744
00:31:20,780 --> 00:31:21,820
Yes, My Lady.

745
00:31:32,600 --> 00:31:33,340
Father...

746
00:31:34,700 --> 00:31:35,750
Father....

747
00:31:48,890 --> 00:31:50,610
Greetings, Father.

748
00:31:53,630 --> 00:31:55,310
What's going on, Tan?

749
00:31:55,340 --> 00:31:57,260
Shouldn't you be more excited?

750
00:32:03,330 --> 00:32:05,470
Fourth Miss is actually ecstatic.

751
00:32:05,490 --> 00:32:06,960
During the five years of your absence,

752
00:32:06,960 --> 00:32:09,130
Fourth Miss never stopped missing you.

753
00:32:09,130 --> 00:32:10,360
She was pleased to hear

754
00:32:10,360 --> 00:32:11,660
that you would come back.

755
00:32:11,660 --> 00:32:12,290
She started

756
00:32:12,290 --> 00:32:13,990
preparing for today's feast 15 days ago.

757
00:32:13,990 --> 00:32:15,400
You've really grown up

758
00:32:15,420 --> 00:32:17,430
in the past five years, Tan.

759
00:32:19,200 --> 00:32:21,280
I left you alone here in the capital

760
00:32:21,280 --> 00:32:22,540
managing the mansion.

761
00:32:22,760 --> 00:32:24,120
That must be hard.

762
00:32:25,040 --> 00:32:26,970
Sorry to have put you through that.

763
00:32:27,700 --> 00:32:29,600
I was just fulfilling my duty.

764
00:32:33,230 --> 00:32:34,280
Uncle, your focus

765
00:32:34,280 --> 00:32:35,240
is entirely on Tan.

766
00:32:35,240 --> 00:32:37,040
You must've forgotten about me.

767
00:32:37,190 --> 00:32:38,840
If it isn't Minmin!

768
00:32:39,050 --> 00:32:40,090
Young lady,

769
00:32:40,120 --> 00:32:41,340
you haven't changed a bit.

770
00:32:41,340 --> 00:32:42,540
Like father,

771
00:32:42,570 --> 00:32:43,730
like daughter.

772
00:32:44,210 --> 00:32:46,570
Of course. She's my daughter after all!

773
00:32:48,970 --> 00:32:52,550
[Duke of Chang]
[Bai Jingyuan]

774
00:32:49,410 --> 00:32:50,210
Old sport,

775
00:32:51,210 --> 00:32:52,480
long time no see.

776
00:32:53,010 --> 00:32:54,270
You're not aging well.

777
00:32:55,380 --> 00:32:57,940
You're leading a comfortable life in the capital.

778
00:32:57,940 --> 00:33:00,160
How can I be compared with you?

779
00:33:01,100 --> 00:33:01,880
Oh, you.

780
00:33:01,880 --> 00:33:03,600
How arrogant of you now.

781
00:33:03,160 --> 00:33:05,070
[Pretty Blossoms]

782
00:33:03,600 --> 00:33:05,000
My dear brother-in-law.

783
00:33:05,450 --> 00:33:07,240
Greetings, Uncle, Auntie.

784
00:33:07,770 --> 00:33:08,430
Tan.

785
00:33:08,630 --> 00:33:10,570
Greetings, Mr. Bai.

786
00:33:12,360 --> 00:33:14,180
My Lord, all the guests have arrived.

787
00:33:14,180 --> 00:33:15,880
Why not go to the dining hall now?

788
00:33:15,880 --> 00:33:17,720
Fourth Miss specifically asked

789
00:33:17,740 --> 00:33:19,840
the kitchen to make a stew for you.

790
00:33:20,130 --> 00:33:20,810
Yes.

791
00:33:20,840 --> 00:33:22,560
Tan didn't sleep well for nights

792
00:33:22,560 --> 00:33:24,160
in order to prepare the stew.

793
00:33:24,280 --> 00:33:25,800
You must try it, Uncle.

794
00:33:25,820 --> 00:33:27,550
It's thoughtful of you, Tan.

795
00:33:27,580 --> 00:33:28,260
Let’s go.

796
00:33:28,890 --> 00:33:29,950
After you, Father.

797
00:33:29,980 --> 00:33:34,710
[Pretty Blossoms]

798
00:33:30,040 --> 00:33:31,480
-Please.
-Let's go!

799
00:33:34,520 --> 00:33:36,780
Didn't sleep well for nights to make a dish?

800
00:33:36,780 --> 00:33:38,140
How ridiculous.

801
00:33:38,840 --> 00:33:40,250
Alright, let's go.

802
00:33:53,880 --> 00:33:54,560
Dig in, guys.

803
00:33:54,560 --> 00:33:55,730
Help yourselves to it.

804
00:33:55,730 --> 00:33:56,560
Father,

805
00:33:56,980 --> 00:33:58,060
try the stew.

806
00:33:58,090 --> 00:33:58,490
Okay.

807
00:33:58,510 --> 00:33:59,770
Find out how it tastes.

808
00:34:00,560 --> 00:34:01,290
Let me try it.

809
00:34:04,820 --> 00:34:06,100
How does it taste?

810
00:34:06,280 --> 00:34:07,540
Tender and delicious.

811
00:34:08,199 --> 00:34:09,840
Very tasty.

812
00:34:11,190 --> 00:34:12,449
I'm glad you like it.

813
00:34:13,000 --> 00:34:13,639
I sure do.

814
00:34:13,800 --> 00:34:14,880
Where are the meat soup

815
00:34:14,880 --> 00:34:16,540
and bamboo shoots I asked for?

816
00:34:16,600 --> 00:34:17,760
I told the kitchen to make those

817
00:34:17,760 --> 00:34:18,699
for me in particular.

818
00:34:18,699 --> 00:34:20,370
Yinxing, tell the kitchen

819
00:34:20,400 --> 00:34:21,360
to make those dishes

820
00:34:21,360 --> 00:34:22,520
right now.

821
00:34:24,010 --> 00:34:24,889
Don't bother.

822
00:34:26,520 --> 00:34:27,550
What do you mean, Tan?

823
00:34:27,550 --> 00:34:28,190
Chu...

824
00:34:28,210 --> 00:34:29,409
Don't I get to eat

825
00:34:29,440 --> 00:34:30,840
and do what I want

826
00:34:30,860 --> 00:34:32,510
at my own home?

827
00:34:32,889 --> 00:34:33,570
Father,

828
00:34:34,050 --> 00:34:34,679
isn't this

829
00:34:34,679 --> 00:34:36,440
supposed to be my home?

830
00:34:36,469 --> 00:34:37,760
She and I are both your daughters.

831
00:34:37,760 --> 00:34:39,120
Do I have to subject myself

832
00:34:39,120 --> 00:34:40,120
to her and be bullied by her?

833
00:34:40,120 --> 00:34:41,120
Alright. Stop it.

834
00:34:41,840 --> 00:34:44,440
Tan, Chu is your sister.

835
00:34:44,800 --> 00:34:46,560
Besides, she is not asking

836
00:34:46,560 --> 00:34:47,679
too much.

837
00:34:48,280 --> 00:34:48,960
Why not...

838
00:34:49,000 --> 00:34:50,600
My Lord, here are the dishes.

839
00:34:54,570 --> 00:34:56,560
The kitchen had already stopped working

840
00:34:56,560 --> 00:34:57,900
when Chu asked for these.

841
00:34:57,900 --> 00:34:59,060
The cooking took

842
00:34:59,090 --> 00:35:00,290
some time.

843
00:35:00,680 --> 00:35:01,720
This is

844
00:35:01,740 --> 00:35:03,220
a welcome feast for

845
00:35:03,300 --> 00:35:04,140
Father, Chu,

846
00:35:04,280 --> 00:35:06,040
and Madam Liu.

847
00:35:06,790 --> 00:35:08,510
Immature though I might be,

848
00:35:08,530 --> 00:35:10,660
I would never treat my family harshly.

849
00:35:13,700 --> 00:35:15,940
Meat soup tastes best when it's warm.

850
00:35:16,530 --> 00:35:17,930
Chu, try it.

851
00:35:25,490 --> 00:35:26,160
Ms. Zhang.

852
00:35:29,680 --> 00:35:30,600
Did I not tell you

853
00:35:30,600 --> 00:35:32,200
to prepare extra tabelware?

854
00:35:32,840 --> 00:35:33,760
Fourth Miss,

855
00:35:34,110 --> 00:35:35,830
I did prepare

856
00:35:35,880 --> 00:35:36,960
some extra.

857
00:35:39,490 --> 00:35:40,850
What a joyous reunion.

858
00:35:41,560 --> 00:35:43,290
But my mother couldn't join us.

859
00:35:44,240 --> 00:35:46,120
So, I found out the tableware

860
00:35:46,120 --> 00:35:47,600
that she used before

861
00:35:51,720 --> 00:35:53,120
and put it on the table

862
00:35:54,310 --> 00:35:56,630
in memory of her.

863
00:36:21,300 --> 00:36:22,650
I shouldn't sit here.

864
00:36:23,990 --> 00:36:25,870
Father, over these years, Mom...

865
00:36:27,580 --> 00:36:28,590
Madam Liu

866
00:36:28,610 --> 00:36:29,760
kept you company in the barren

867
00:36:29,760 --> 00:36:30,730
Yangxi Prefecture.

868
00:36:30,730 --> 00:36:31,850
She suffered a lot.

869
00:36:31,870 --> 00:36:32,880
Why can't she eat

870
00:36:32,880 --> 00:36:34,480
at the same table as us?

871
00:36:35,160 --> 00:36:36,080
The customs in the capital

872
00:36:36,080 --> 00:36:37,840
are different from those in the army.

873
00:36:37,840 --> 00:36:38,640
I believe

874
00:36:39,560 --> 00:36:40,760
Madam Liu

875
00:36:40,760 --> 00:36:42,280
is a sensible person.

876
00:36:45,120 --> 00:36:46,600
But we're home now.

877
00:36:46,600 --> 00:36:48,130
Why talk about rigid rules?

878
00:36:49,420 --> 00:36:50,520
Chu and Madam Liu

879
00:36:50,520 --> 00:36:52,350
spent years with you in the border area.

880
00:36:52,350 --> 00:36:54,350
I could only imagine how hard it was.

881
00:36:54,480 --> 00:36:56,300
These customs are often ignored in the army.

882
00:36:56,300 --> 00:36:58,670
Father must have been very tolerant of

883
00:36:58,700 --> 00:37:00,300
Madam Liu and Chu in the past.

884
00:37:00,320 --> 00:37:01,800
But now we're in the capital.

885
00:37:01,800 --> 00:37:03,480
Both nobles and commoners

886
00:37:03,480 --> 00:37:05,140
observe certain traditions.

887
00:37:05,280 --> 00:37:07,040
As Madam Liu said to me just now,

888
00:37:07,330 --> 00:37:09,970
there are strict rules in the mansion.

889
00:37:10,050 --> 00:37:11,850
If word gets out about our bad manners,

890
00:37:11,850 --> 00:37:13,080
people will criticize us

891
00:37:13,080 --> 00:37:14,380
for being uncivilized.

892
00:37:14,380 --> 00:37:15,300
It will tarnish

893
00:37:16,440 --> 00:37:17,970
Father's good reputation.

894
00:37:18,530 --> 00:37:18,970
How...

895
00:37:19,000 --> 00:37:19,960
How am I tarnishing

896
00:37:19,960 --> 00:37:21,490
Father's good reputation?

897
00:37:22,440 --> 00:37:23,970
Shortly after your return,

898
00:37:24,320 --> 00:37:26,120
you punished my maid.

899
00:37:26,760 --> 00:37:28,560
I heard that you even argued

900
00:37:28,580 --> 00:37:29,460
with Ms. Zhang

901
00:37:29,730 --> 00:37:31,190
and nearly assaulted her.

902
00:37:31,520 --> 00:37:33,300
I was disciplining those servants,

903
00:37:33,300 --> 00:37:34,280
so they would remember

904
00:37:34,280 --> 00:37:35,640
their roles here.

905
00:37:36,020 --> 00:37:38,320
Ms. Zhang refused to open the main entrance.

906
00:37:38,320 --> 00:37:39,790
She insisted that we use the side door.

907
00:37:39,790 --> 00:37:41,790
She was purposefully demeaning...

908
00:37:41,880 --> 00:37:42,930
me and Madam Liu.

909
00:37:43,080 --> 00:37:44,180
Then, that maid Lyu'e

910
00:37:44,180 --> 00:37:45,400
provoked me.

911
00:37:45,460 --> 00:37:46,920
She deserved punishment.

912
00:37:47,770 --> 00:37:49,740
Lyu'e is my personal maid.

913
00:37:49,860 --> 00:37:51,520
She always behaves properly.

914
00:37:51,850 --> 00:37:54,290
Ms. Zhang abides by the rules all the time.

915
00:37:55,100 --> 00:37:56,900
She's an important housekeeper

916
00:37:57,120 --> 00:37:59,320
who has worked here for most of her life.

917
00:37:59,380 --> 00:38:01,050
But you lashed out at her

918
00:38:01,070 --> 00:38:03,610
and shoved her outside the mansion.

919
00:38:03,900 --> 00:38:05,930
Our family reputation and Father's good name

920
00:38:05,930 --> 00:38:07,730
would possibly be compromised.

921
00:38:18,960 --> 00:38:20,690
Father's return to the capital

922
00:38:20,920 --> 00:38:22,480
must have attracted much attention.

923
00:38:22,480 --> 00:38:23,680
We're being watched.

924
00:38:24,330 --> 00:38:25,950
As females,

925
00:38:25,980 --> 00:38:27,360
though we can't help Father

926
00:38:27,360 --> 00:38:28,760
with political affairs,

927
00:38:29,380 --> 00:38:31,270
we should be reasonable

928
00:38:31,680 --> 00:38:32,840
and think twice

929
00:38:33,370 --> 00:38:34,970
before we say or do anything.

930
00:38:36,850 --> 00:38:39,000
Tan is right.

931
00:38:39,160 --> 00:38:39,760
Father!

932
00:38:39,760 --> 00:38:40,680
Enough.

933
00:38:41,230 --> 00:38:43,120
You're acting like a child now.

934
00:38:43,200 --> 00:38:44,800
What Tan said is correct.

935
00:38:45,200 --> 00:38:46,240
You should learn

936
00:38:46,240 --> 00:38:47,480
from your sister.

937
00:38:53,810 --> 00:38:55,960
Aren't we here to welcome

938
00:38:55,960 --> 00:38:57,040
your return?

939
00:38:57,040 --> 00:38:57,520
Why are we

940
00:38:57,520 --> 00:38:58,680
talking about raising children?

941
00:38:58,680 --> 00:39:00,120
Save it for later.

942
00:39:00,320 --> 00:39:01,720
Your uncle is right.

943
00:39:02,000 --> 00:39:04,280
This is a reunion.

944
00:39:05,160 --> 00:39:06,360
Let's have

945
00:39:06,640 --> 00:39:08,840
a gathering feast as a family.

946
00:39:13,080 --> 00:39:13,640
My Lady,

947
00:39:13,960 --> 00:39:15,440
this letter just arrived.

948
00:39:15,680 --> 00:39:17,480
It is said to be important to you.

949
00:39:19,560 --> 00:39:21,960
Who sent it to me?

950
00:39:19,730 --> 00:39:21,530
[For Ming Tan]

951
00:39:21,960 --> 00:39:23,640
The owner of Wentao Pavilion.

952
00:39:24,640 --> 00:39:25,520
Wentao?

953
00:39:28,120 --> 00:39:29,680
The guard working for the Liang family,

954
00:39:29,680 --> 00:39:31,160
Chen Si, who pushed you into water

955
00:39:31,160 --> 00:39:33,480
in the Lantern Festival is hiding in the west room of Wentao Pavilion now.

956
00:39:31,620 --> 00:39:34,350
[Wentao Pavilion]

957
00:39:41,060 --> 00:39:42,580
Why did you give the letter

958
00:39:42,650 --> 00:39:44,050
to Miss Ming instead of

959
00:39:44,590 --> 00:39:46,390
Marquis of Jing'an?

960
00:39:48,600 --> 00:39:49,860
Just to avoid trouble.

961
00:39:50,170 --> 00:39:51,520
If you had sent the letter

962
00:39:51,520 --> 00:39:52,720
to the marquis,

963
00:39:53,230 --> 00:39:54,560
He would get suspicious

964
00:39:54,880 --> 00:39:56,400
and start a investigation.

965
00:39:56,400 --> 00:39:58,020
It could save you much trouble

966
00:39:58,020 --> 00:39:59,980
by sending the letter to Miss Ming instead.

967
00:39:59,980 --> 00:40:01,840
If it weren't for the Ming family,

968
00:40:02,340 --> 00:40:04,740
I would've put the Duke of Ling into prison.

969
00:40:05,840 --> 00:40:08,250
Marquis of Jing'an's is a rarely seen talent.

970
00:40:08,250 --> 00:40:09,310
If he became in-laws

971
00:40:09,310 --> 00:40:10,750
with the Duke of Ling,

972
00:40:10,870 --> 00:40:12,030
things would be tough for us.

973
00:40:12,030 --> 00:40:13,830
Fortunately, Miss Ming is smart

974
00:40:13,850 --> 00:40:14,850
and decisive.

975
00:40:14,900 --> 00:40:18,160
Otherwise, it would take us more time to solve the problem.

976
00:40:22,480 --> 00:40:23,280
What on earth

977
00:40:23,280 --> 00:40:25,210
happened in the Lantern Festival?

978
00:40:25,720 --> 00:40:26,560
Father,

979
00:40:26,930 --> 00:40:28,710
I went out for fun that night.

980
00:40:28,780 --> 00:40:30,500
Someone from the Liang family bumped into me.

981
00:40:30,500 --> 00:40:32,160
I ended up falling into water.

982
00:40:32,980 --> 00:40:34,620
The Liang family did it

983
00:40:34,860 --> 00:40:37,020
to make me marry Liang Zixuan quickly.

984
00:40:37,650 --> 00:40:39,350
Luckily, I can swim.

985
00:40:39,480 --> 00:40:41,880
So, Liang Zixuan didn't get what he wanted.

986
00:40:42,700 --> 00:40:45,460
How absurd and despicable!

987
00:40:45,500 --> 00:40:46,580
Shame on them.

988
00:40:46,880 --> 00:40:48,600
Does your godfather know about this?

989
00:40:48,600 --> 00:40:49,840
I thought

990
00:40:49,860 --> 00:40:51,770
we should find out the truth first,

991
00:40:51,770 --> 00:40:53,300
so I didn't tell Godfather.

992
00:40:53,560 --> 00:40:54,880
I only knew that Minmin came

993
00:40:54,880 --> 00:40:56,530
home late in the Lantern Festival.

994
00:40:56,530 --> 00:40:58,460
I didn't know you got in danger.

995
00:40:58,480 --> 00:41:00,360
How could you two hide

996
00:41:00,480 --> 00:41:01,830
something so important from us?

997
00:41:01,830 --> 00:41:03,790
We didn't want to worry you.

998
00:41:04,520 --> 00:41:06,780
This matter is only known to a few people.

999
00:41:07,040 --> 00:41:09,200
The less it's heard, the better.

1000
00:41:11,090 --> 00:41:12,690
Tan, don’t worry.

1001
00:41:12,720 --> 00:41:13,920
I will seek justice

1002
00:41:13,940 --> 00:41:14,820
for you.

1003
00:41:25,600 --> 00:41:26,240
D-Don't kill me!

1004
00:41:26,240 --> 00:41:26,700
Tell me!

1005
00:41:27,000 --> 00:41:28,080
What did you do?

1006
00:41:28,160 --> 00:41:29,440
I-I didn't do anything.

1007
00:41:29,440 --> 00:41:31,000
Then what about the incident

1008
00:41:31,000 --> 00:41:32,000
in the Lantern Festival?

1009
00:41:32,000 --> 00:41:32,600
Say it!

1010
00:41:32,600 --> 00:41:33,230
I...

1011
00:41:33,490 --> 00:41:34,960
I pushed Miss Ming into water

1012
00:41:34,960 --> 00:41:36,440
at my master's request.

1013
00:41:36,460 --> 00:41:38,790
I have nothing to do with the rest!

1014
00:41:39,200 --> 00:41:40,520
Liang Qiwei...

1015
00:41:41,580 --> 00:41:42,940
What a punk!

1016
00:41:44,640 --> 00:41:45,480
Have the Liang family

1017
00:41:45,480 --> 00:41:46,530
gone crazy?

1018
00:41:46,680 --> 00:41:48,220
Tan already got engaged to Zixuan.

1019
00:41:48,220 --> 00:41:49,460
When you came back,

1020
00:41:49,600 --> 00:41:51,200
they could get married soon.

1021
00:41:51,360 --> 00:41:52,820
Why must they pull a trick?

1022
00:41:53,000 --> 00:41:54,230
Liang Zixuan and his cousin

1023
00:41:54,230 --> 00:41:55,830
were in a relationship.

1024
00:41:56,080 --> 00:41:56,800
Now,

1025
00:41:56,800 --> 00:41:58,280
they have a son.

1026
00:41:58,560 --> 00:41:59,080
W-What?

1027
00:41:59,080 --> 00:42:00,680
The Liang family was afraid that you'd hear about it

1028
00:42:00,680 --> 00:42:01,930
and cancel the engagement.

1029
00:42:01,930 --> 00:42:03,320
They planned to let Zixuan

1030
00:42:03,320 --> 00:42:04,280
save me from drowning,

1031
00:42:04,280 --> 00:42:05,840
so I had to marry him.

1032
00:42:07,920 --> 00:42:09,080
Why didn't you tell me

1033
00:42:09,080 --> 00:42:10,760
about this serious matter?

1034
00:42:10,760 --> 00:42:12,240
I heard that the Liang family had connections

1035
00:42:12,240 --> 00:42:13,260
with the Ministry of Personnel.

1036
00:42:13,260 --> 00:42:14,520
I know little about politics.

1037
00:42:14,520 --> 00:42:15,920
I was afraid that your career

1038
00:42:15,920 --> 00:42:16,840
and transfer back to the capital

1039
00:42:16,840 --> 00:42:18,840
would be affected if I canceled the engagement.

1040
00:42:18,840 --> 00:42:19,080
So...

1041
00:42:19,080 --> 00:42:21,140
The Liang family means nothing to me.

1042
00:42:21,160 --> 00:42:22,920
They can't affect my career!

1043
00:42:23,110 --> 00:42:23,800
Guards!

1044
00:42:25,840 --> 00:42:27,600
I'll cancel the engagement now.

1045
00:42:27,600 --> 00:42:28,400
No, no.

1046
00:42:28,400 --> 00:42:29,800
I'm not going there!

1047
00:42:29,820 --> 00:42:30,620
I'm not!

1048
00:42:38,880 --> 00:42:40,210
It went as you expected.

1049
00:42:40,560 --> 00:42:43,000
The Liang family resorted to devious means

1050
00:42:43,040 --> 00:42:44,520
to secure the engagement.

1051
00:42:44,800 --> 00:42:46,260
How could they give up now?

1052
00:42:47,360 --> 00:42:48,840
Maybe even the marquis

1053
00:42:48,960 --> 00:42:51,520
can't cancel the engagement.

1054
00:42:56,690 --> 00:42:59,390
[Profound Virtue and Boundless Grace]

1055
00:43:00,280 --> 00:43:01,280
Say something!

1056
00:43:02,690 --> 00:43:03,720
It was Zixuan who

1057
00:43:03,720 --> 00:43:05,120
fell into water that day.

1058
00:43:05,280 --> 00:43:07,440
Everyone in the capital knows it.

1059
00:43:07,460 --> 00:43:08,360
Exactly.

1060
00:43:08,360 --> 00:43:09,840
The fact that we came here

1061
00:43:10,410 --> 00:43:11,590
means we have found out

1062
00:43:11,590 --> 00:43:12,590
the whole truth.

1063
00:43:12,980 --> 00:43:14,600
Love can't be forced.

1064
00:43:14,800 --> 00:43:16,120
It'll be the best if you could

1065
00:43:16,120 --> 00:43:17,360
just let us cancel

1066
00:43:17,560 --> 00:43:18,840
the engagement.

1067
00:43:20,210 --> 00:43:22,080
If people know Ming Tan fell into water,

1068
00:43:22,080 --> 00:43:24,620
her reputation will be damaged.

1069
00:43:27,600 --> 00:43:28,320
You see,

1070
00:43:28,640 --> 00:43:29,880
we are about

1071
00:43:29,880 --> 00:43:31,280
to become in-laws.

1072
00:43:31,440 --> 00:43:32,840
Why are you so mad

1073
00:43:32,840 --> 00:43:34,000
about something that hasn't

1074
00:43:34,000 --> 00:43:34,880
been proven?

1075
00:43:34,880 --> 00:43:35,640
Yeah.

1076
00:43:35,640 --> 00:43:37,440
Someone must be jealous of

1077
00:43:37,440 --> 00:43:38,760
our bond,

1078
00:43:38,780 --> 00:43:40,900
so this person

1079
00:43:40,930 --> 00:43:42,570
set us up.

1080
00:43:42,590 --> 00:43:43,820
The entire Liang family

1081
00:43:43,820 --> 00:43:45,120
thinks highly of Ming Tan.

1082
00:43:45,120 --> 00:43:46,110
When she marries our son,

1083
00:43:46,110 --> 00:43:48,170
I will treat her like my own daughter,

1084
00:43:48,170 --> 00:43:50,610
and not upset her in any way.

1085
00:43:50,880 --> 00:43:52,280
I have a witness here.

1086
00:43:52,350 --> 00:43:53,790
How dare you deny it?

1087
00:43:53,810 --> 00:43:54,940
It's bold of you two!

1088
00:43:57,680 --> 00:43:58,880
I know that your niece

1089
00:43:59,000 --> 00:43:59,840
had a long stay

1090
00:43:59,840 --> 00:44:01,280
in your house.

1091
00:44:01,920 --> 00:44:03,680
She was involved with your son

1092
00:44:03,680 --> 00:44:04,600
and got pregnant!

